<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{ app_name }}</title>
    <style>
        /* S-Store Email Design System */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #212529;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #212529;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #212529;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background-color: #e0e7ff;
            border: 1px solid #1e3a8a;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .info-box strong {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #1e3a8a;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #dee2e6;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 24px 16px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 24px 16px;
            }
            
            .footer {
                padding: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="logo">{{ app_name }}</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome aboard!</h2>
            
            <p>Hi {{ user_name }},</p>
            
            <p>We're excited to have you join {{ app_name }}. Your account has been successfully created and you're ready to get started.</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Your account email:</strong> {{ user_email }}</p>
            </div>
            
            {{ if login_url }}
            <p>Click the button below to access your account:</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ login_url }}" class="button">Access Your Account</a>
            </p>
            {{ end }}
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Best regards,<br><strong>The {{ app_name }} Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ current_year }} {{ app_name }}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
